      "content": "interesting. for the dealer character, you mentioned black or hispanic. if we wanted to make the show feel even more hyper-realistic and gritty, would there be any specific physical traits or certain 'looks' associated with those backgrounds that would help the audience immediately identify them as being from that specific environment? like, what would make the casting feel more 'authentic' to that vibe?",
